name: AirportLookup
0:
”Alexa open Airport Lookup”
”Alexa tell Airport Lookup to look up Boston”
”Alexa ask Airport Lookup to look up Phoenix”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: airport lookup
des: This skill looks up airport information based on airport name or airport code. If airport name is used, the skill tries its best to "guess" the intended airport, and then get the status of that airport. If no US airport is found, the skill provides an error message.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
